Build: 
# make

Run: 
1. insert module on server A: "insmod ntbtest.ko addr=0x4; rmmod ntbtest"
2. Dump memory on server B: "od -x --skip-bytes=0x4 --read-bytes=4 /dev/mem"

The output of od on the B server should increment each time the module is 
inserted on the A server.

Before:
0000004 eef3 f000
0000010

After:
0000004 eef4 f000
0000010 